name: Rabbits vs Raccoons
description:
Defeat all the raccoons in a "whack em all" unlimited experience. Raccoons and rabbits are coming out of holes in the ground and you must get as many as you can before they take over everything.

Play on your Web Browser or download it for your Android device (KitKat version / API 19 or above).
